{"tid":1552641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拖手攻略]9.9全港中學聯校人鏈 校友家長同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:41:25.000Z","uid":303513,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f5e6b4ffdec61277ad5d8e5e0842e145c2bd4c","tid":1552641,"uid":303513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拖手都要有策略！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人鏈最主要都係比返工搭車嗰堆人睇到香港人嘅決心，小妹我前幾日返母校築人鏈有少少心得想分享下：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 黎得一陣都好，最緊要有參與過</strong><br />\n- 最理想就係0730企好曬，全程好多校友都會早走遲到，人鏈嘅目的都係聲援罷課學生，多你一個係一個，少你一個都係一個，比師弟妹知道有好多人撐佢地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 盡量企開d</strong><br />\n-  眼見好多人膊頭貼膊頭咁企，做乜姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雙手有長度架，spread開d企啦，人鏈越長越好！怕熱唔想拖可以拎住文宣單張兩邊，用其他嘢隔開都得。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 企位分配</strong><br />\n- 校友自己醒水搵啱地方企，各校校門之間嗰d位好需要你。我見有po<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">呼籲學生遲5分鐘入學校</span></span>，呢d睇學生個人意願啦，比佢地企近校門方last minute衝入去。<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好企出馬路！綠燈先企出去！</span>喺冇紅綠燈嘅馬路適當咁斷開係可接受嘅。阻住馬路只會令更多學生校友趕唔到返學/返黎支持。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 嗌口號</strong><br />\n- 有時喺馬路旁邊車聲好嘈，根本聽唔到口號嗰d，最好定個pattern，例如按「光復香港時代革命&mdash;&gt;五大訴求缺一不可&mdash;&gt;沒有暴徒只有暴政&mdash;&gt;香港警察知法犯法&mdash;&gt;香港人加油」呢個順序，每個slogan嗌3次就轉下一個，帶頭嗌嘅人口乾冇氣想唞下嘅其他人都知道接住嗌乜<br />\n- 遇著學校附近係民居，有學校會選擇某幾個時間點先叫口號，各自配合啦呢d<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 唱歌</strong><br />\n- 建議大概0740呢d時間唱Do you hear the people sing，因為返學人潮最多，亦可能會無端端興起唱校歌，唔記得歌詞就search定mark低喺手機啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇著d送仔女返學嘅家長講d難聽說話，希望大家盡量禁住脾氣，君子動口不動手啊，大聲d嗌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><ins></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 加油</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大概係咁多，麻煩大家幫手推！有咩補充歡迎留言！"},{"pid":"12b45fdeb176d0a629d7222dc31aef65787dc9b0","tid":1552641,"uid":303513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"沙田區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZ4JL5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZ4JL5f.jpg&h=deb42994&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zazYzYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzazYzYA.jpg&h=a9a074e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oL5Qq5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoL5Qq5f.jpg&h=f6d326a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLaT8iG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLaT8iG.jpg&h=1ba10665&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rj1W55n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frj1W55n.jpg&h=9b07b3ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca9c503ced3fc3cc301077f5ee72c00376ac7345","tid":1552641,"uid":303513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"元朗區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnakOjq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnakOjq.jpg&h=7e993847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qN8nhcL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqN8nhcL.jpg&h=acdea873&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11c38de0e77464e19fba9a3d814b05527901a86b","tid":1552641,"uid":303513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"北區<br />\n<img src=\"h